These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: san-franciscopy, marigold, aconite
City: rome, prague, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to prague is the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growsaconite is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who growsmarigold##2
3. the person who growssan-franciscopy is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Flower      | marigold | aconite | san-franciscopy |
| City   | prague     | rome    | san-francisco   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, western, martial-arts
3 different games are played: scrabble, whist, canasta
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the person playing scrabble and the person watching time-travel movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | martial-arts        | western |
| Game     | whist | canasta | scrabble         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
City: paris, prague, rome
There are 3 different nationalities: british, mexican, brazilian
1. the british is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to paris is between the mexican and the person traveling to rome##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| City   | prague | paris     | rome |
| Nationality        | mexican  | brazilian | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade
City: san-francisco, prague, miami
1. the person drinking 7up is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage   | coffee  | lemonade     | 7up |
| City           | prague | miami | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, grey, purple
House: wooden, colonial, ranch-style
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the wooden house is between the ranch-style house and the colonial house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Color   | grey | purple     | mauve |
| House     | ranch-style    | wooden | colonial    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, brown, lilac
House: colonial, cottage, wooden
1. the colonial house is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes chestnut##2
2. the person who likes chestnut is the cottage house##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Color   | chestnut  | brown   | lilac        |
| House         | cottage | colonial | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
House: farmhouse, cottage, victorian
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
1. the victorian house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is between the victorian house and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| House          | cottage  | farmhouse  | victorian |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | mirinda | sprite     |

