.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, rock, country
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, fishing, woodworking
1. the fan rock is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the fan rock and the fan country##2
3. the fan rock is on the right of the fan trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | country   | trance  | rock  |
| Hobby   | dancing | fishing | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, drawing, sudoku
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, daffodil
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who growstulip is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who growsdaisy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Hobby       | sudoku | camping | drawing  |
| Flower   | daffodil    | tulip        | daisy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, aristoff, bluemaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, parkour, skiing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who's sport is skiing and the blend-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | aristoff | blend |
| Sport   | skiing     | basketball    | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, van, train
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is between the person driving the van and the person watching adventure movies##2
2. the person driving the train is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Transport   | van | car      | train      |
| Movie-Genre       | horror  | scientific | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
