There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, turquise, aquamarine
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes turquise##2
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | montecristo   | chaman   |
| Color         | turquise | aquamarine | coral |

