.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, drama
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, november, april
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person watching epic movies and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | disaster   | drama  |
| Birthday        | november | may | april |

