.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, train, bike
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo, montecristo
1. the bongani-smoker is between the person driving the train and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the train is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Transport   | train | van   | bike   |
| Cigar         | montecristo  | bongani | tiparillo |

