.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-17::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, frog
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, july, august
1. the owner of the frog is between the person who's birthday is in july and the owner of the rabbit##2
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Pet   | rabbit       | frog | horse |
| Birthday         | october | august | july      |

 #################################

 
