.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, iris
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, lilac, grey
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growsiris and the person who likes lilac##2
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Flower      | iris | orchid   | tulip |
| Color   | grey  | yellow | lilac   |

 